name: Self Portrait at Zeta's Bodymod Parlour (during Neurotronics installation) [Cryptoborg #9]
description: The Bodymod Parlour is a chromium plated junk store full of second-hand body parts, thrift-store technocosmetics, cranial neurographs and memory upgrades catering to the – in-fashion – nihilo-cypher neosavage aesthetics.
